content: I think I'll go with the KVARTERSKLIPPER shelf from IKEA. It seems like a great option for holding my small planters and adding a touch of elegance to my living room. And, I'll add a small decorative box to the shelf to add some visual interest. Thanks for the suggestion! By the way, have you heard about the great deals you can find at Goodwill? I recently scored a like-new pair of skinny jeans for $12, and I've been wearing them nonstop.
